data.description: Great opportunity located in the amenity filled Bayshore community. This is a three bedroom, one bath home. Many updates have been made to this home to make it move in ready including the flooring, a/c system, bathroom, water heater and a new roof was just installed. The home offers a spacious open concept floor plan which opens up to a huge fenced in backyard to host family gatherings! There is also plenty of parking for your boat or RV. The home also offers a one stall garage, Optional features in the Bayshore community include a private marina, boat ramp, community center, swimming pool, park, picnic areas, fishing areas, a basketball court, baseball field and more! And all of these amenities are walking distance from the home. Bayshore Gardens is also updating some of these amenities to make them even more enjoyable for everyone in the community!
